This is the wiki page for [http://gotgenes.com Chris Lasher], a.k.a. '''gotgenes'''. Chris currently works as a graduate research assistant at [http://www.vt.edu Virginia Tech], specifically at the [https://www.vbi.vt.edu Virginia Bioinformatics Institute]. He uses and supports the [http://biopython.org BioPython] project, and advocates and contributes to [http://swc.scipy.org Software Carpentry], a course created by [http://third-bit.com Dr. Greg Wilson] to demonstrate good development practices to scientists and engineers.